text: Sad news. I will not have the swag I intended to have - vendors were not able to produce it in time. Please do still come visit me at the Spin Group booth in the developer Science fair and I will tell you, and can show you, what we have coming down the road for the extension!

Because a fair amount of time was spent designing them. The gifty was going to be some great stickers. <https://spin.d.pr/qUX1yU+> (all were going to be circular)

 If you’re interested in printing your own sticker I can provide the files. Sorry that it wasn’t here in time for inbound.

Again visit me at the Developer Science Fair to see and hear about what we’re working on to make the tool even better. We have some things in progress I think you’ll love -- almost as much as the developer menu, dark theme and cache buster.
